********** WIND PRESSURE CALCULATIONS **********
* WIND SPEED, Vb= 33 M/SEC
* RISK COEFFICIENT, K1 = 1
* TERRAIN, HEIGHT FACTOR, K2 = 1
* TOPOGRAPHY FACTOR, K3 = 1
* IMP FACTOR FOR CYCLONIC REGION, K4 = 1
* DESIGN WIND SPEED AT HEIGHT z, Vz = Vb * K1 * K2 * K3 * K4 * x = 33 * 1 * 1 * 1 * 1 * 1 = 33 m/s
* WIND PRESSURE AT HEIGHT z, Pz = 0.6 * Vz^2 = 0.6 * 33^2 = 653.4 N/m2 = 0.654 KN/M2
* WIND DIRECTIONALITY FACTOR, Kd = 0.9
* AREA AVERAGING FACTOR, Ka = 0.8 ~ FOR RAFTER
* AREA AVERAGING FACTOR, Ka = 0.846 ~ FOR COLUMN
* COMBINATION FACTOR, Kc = 0.9
* DESIGN WIND PRESSURE, Pd = Kd*Ka*Kc*Pz = 0.458 ~ FOR RAFTER
* DESIGN WIND PRESSURE, Pd = Kd*Ka*Kc*Pz = 0.458 ~ FOR COLUMN
* INTERNAL PRESSURE COEFFICIENT = +/- 0.5
* EXTERNAL PRESSURE COEFF'S FROM IS875-III TABLES
